'''1-硝基萘'''是一种[[有机化合物|有机化合物]]，化学式为C<sub>10</sub>H<sub>7</sub>NO<sub>2</sub>。它可由[[萘|萘]]的硝化反应制备，[[硝酸|硝]][[硫酸|硫]]混酸是最常见的硝化试剂，<ref>Khabarov, Yu. G.; Veshnyakov, V. A.; Snigirev, I. A. Method for producing 1-nitronaphthalene. 2018. RU 2669774 C1.</ref><ref>{{cite book|location=Weinheim, Germany|language=en|isbn=9783527306732|publisher=Wiley-VCH Verlag GmbH & Co. KGaA|date=2000-06-15|url=http://doi.wiley.com/10.1002/14356007.a17_009|title=Naphthalene Derivatives|accessdate=2020-12-28|editor= Wiley-VCH Verlag GmbH & Co. KGaA|author=Gerald Booth|doi=10.1002/14356007.a17_009}}</ref>也有文献报道使用[[硝酸铋|硝酸铋]]<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Tetrahedron Letters|volume=41|issue=42|language=en|date=2000-10|pages=8017–8020|doi=10.1016/S0040-4039(00)01397-6|url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0040403900013976|title=Surface-mediated highly efficient regioselective nitration of aromatic compounds by bismuth nitrate|accessdate=2020-12-28|author=Susanta Samajdar, Frederick F Becker, Bimal K Banik|archive-date=2018-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180627230654/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0040403900013976|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[二氧化氮|二氧化氮]]<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Research on Chemical Intermediates|volume=41|issue=11|language=en|issn=0922-6168|date=2015-11|pages=8307–8315|doi=10.1007/s11164-014-1893-1|url=http://link.springer.com/10.1007/s11164-014-1893-1|title=A simple approach for preparation of dinitronaphthalene compounds from the nitration reaction of 1-nitronaphthalene with NO2 as nitration reagent|accessdate=2020-12-28|author=Kuiyi You, Zhongcang Zhou, Jian Jian, Renjie Deng, Pingle Liu, Qiuhong Ai, He’an Luo}}</ref>、''N''-硝基糖精<!-- CAS 80283-99-4 --><ref>{{cite journal|journal=Nature Communications|volume=10|issue=1|language=en|issn=2041-1723|date=2019-12|doi=10.1038/s41467-019-11419-y|url=http://www.nature.com/articles/s41467-019-11419-y|title=Facile access to nitroarenes and nitroheteroarenes using N-nitrosaccharin|accessdate=2020-12-28|author=Roxan Calvo, Kun Zhang, Alessandro Passera, Dmitry Katayev|pmid=31363083|pmc=PMC6667458|archive-date=2019-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191115090000/https://www.nature.com/articles/s41467-019-11419-y|dead-url=no}}</ref>等进行硝化反应。它可以被还原剂（如[[氢气|氢气]]<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Molecular Catalysis|volume=494|language=en|date=2020-10|pages=111151|doi=10.1016/j.mcat.2020.111151|url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S2468823120304144|title=PtNi/C bimetallic nanocatalyst with high catalytic performance and stability for 1-nitronaphthalene hydorgenation to 1-naphthylamine|accessdate=2020-12-28|author=Huan Fu, Luna Ruan, Jianhua Liao, An Pei, Jun Liu, Li Zeng, Kai Yang, Lihua Zhu, Bing Hui Chen}}</ref>、[[硼氢化钠|硼氢化钠]]<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Scientific Reports|volume=10|issue=1|language=en|issn=2045-2322|date=2020-12|doi=10.1038/s41598-020-64988-0|url=http://www.nature.com/articles/s41598-020-64988-0|title=A Novel Hydrogenation of Nitroarene Compounds with Multi Wall Carbon Nanotube Supported Palladium/Copper Nanoparticles (PdCu@MWCNT NPs) in Aqueous Medium|accessdate=2020-12-28|author=Haydar Göksu, Nursefa Zengin, Hakan Burhan, Kemal Cellat, Fatih Şen|pmid=32415148|pmc=PMC7229225|archive-date=2021-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211002190603/https://www.nature.com/articles/s41598-020-64988-0}}</ref>、[[水合肼|水合肼]]<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Chemistry - A European Journal|volume=17|issue=21|language=en|date=2011-05-16|pages=5903–5907|doi=10.1002/chem.201003621|url=http://doi.wiley.com/10.1002/chem.201003621|title=Phosphane-Free Green Protocol for Selective Nitro Reduction with an Iron-Based Catalyst|accessdate=2020-12-28|author=Upendra Sharma, Praveen Kumar Verma, Neeraj Kumar, Vishal Kumar, Manju Bala, Bikram Singh}}</ref>等）还原为[[1-萘胺|1-萘胺]]。

